Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.53,0:01:37.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目  等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.07,0:01:41.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里签名吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.84,0:01:42.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,签名？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.70,0:01:46.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要在旧校舍搞什么活动吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.89,0:01:47.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,试胆大会
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.51,0:01:50.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fe128\fscx80\fscy92\fnDFPTFLeiSho-W5}笹{\r}田
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.01,0:01:54.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不聚集一定的人数就无法拿到使用许可
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.71,0:01:55.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮帮忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.81,0:01:58.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉很有趣吧  是{\fe128\fscx80\fscy92\fnDFPTFLeiSho-W5}笹{\r}田的提议
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.55,0:01:59.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.27,0:02:00.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.66,0:02:06.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.24,0:02:07.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.60,0:02:09.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很意外吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.07,0:02:15.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也没想到高傲的班长要举办鬼怪大会
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.90,0:02:17.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.45,0:02:22.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那确定后跟你联系
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.30,0:02:24.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.73,0:02:27.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.83,0:02:34.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然看不见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.20,0:02:39.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟…糟了  再见
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.02,0:02:40.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.16,0:02:42.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙怎么了  突然慌慌张张的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.51,0:02:48.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.18,0:03:00.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不追过来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.45,0:03:03.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.79,0:03:07.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是夏目玲子大人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.65,0:03:11.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  玲子是我祖母  她已经去世了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.24,0:03:13.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把友人帐交出来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.27,0:03:16.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不交出来就吃了你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.47,0:03:18.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.30,0:03:20.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猫咪老师
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.88,0:03:22.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别妨碍我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.38,0:03:27.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是你这种低级妖怪能使用的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.88,0:03:28.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住口
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.87,0:03:33.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且有他死后友人帐归我的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.93,0:03:35.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说我已经预约了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.82,0:03:37.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖乖消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.25,0:03:42.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要消失的是你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.31,0:03:45.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.85,0:03:48.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滚吧  不知天高地厚的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.81,0:03:55.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  解决了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.17,0:03:57.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你  老师
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.19,0:04:02.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢礼就要七{\fe128\fscx80\fscy92\fnDFPTFLeiSho-W5}辻{\r}屋的包子好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.27,0:04:04.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很喜欢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.56,0:04:10.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为友人帐而找上门的妖怪有两种
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.17,0:04:18.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一种是像刚才一样想统治被写了名字的妖怪而来抢友人帐的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.10,0:04:21.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一种则是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.39,0:04:24.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.10,0:04:28.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来讨回写在友人帐上的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.65,0:04:37.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个包子多少都吃得下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.50,0:04:41.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  又归还名字了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.99,0:04:42.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.97,0:04:44.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是多此一举
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.33,0:04:47.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,友人帐越来越薄了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.39,0:04:51.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,归还名字后非常疲惫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.22,0:05:00.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我拿到时还能剩几只呢  干脆吃了这小鬼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.52,0:05:03.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听到了哦  你这只冒牌招财猫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.59,0:05:08.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.24,0:05:10.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多吃点哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.15,0:05:14.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔子阿姨开朗而温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.30,0:05:17.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滋叔叔话比较少  但一直很温和
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.82,0:05:21.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不想给他们添麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.88,0:05:26.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不吃呢  猫咪它
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.02,0:05:33.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  这可添了个大麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.37,0:05:36.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它不吃剩饭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.52,0:05:37.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.76,0:05:42.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.45,0:05:44.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的呢  看来是个美食家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.57,0:05:45.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.23,0:05:50.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？这是牙痕？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.79,0:05:54.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟  真是美味啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.03,0:05:58.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  贵志
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.46,0:06:00.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不小心呛到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.74,0:06:05.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸好塔子阿姨他们看不见
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.47,0:06:09.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目大人  请把名字还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.28,0:06:11.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.48,0:06:15.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仔细一看你不是露神老头吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.99,0:06:18.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认识他吗  老师
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.90,0:06:22.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  因为变小了我没认出来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.02,0:06:23.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  这个声音是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.21,0:06:26.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊  你是斑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.11,0:06:31.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么变成这副可笑的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.08,0:06:32.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喵啰嗦  我吃了你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.02,0:06:35.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.32,0:06:40.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾之守护哟  昭显其名
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.14,0:06:49.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.64,0:06:53.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  跟后面一张粘在一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.44,0:06:56.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的呢  完全粘在一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.19,0:06:58.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是米粒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.02,0:06:59.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米粒？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.31,0:07:04.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲子总是马马虎虎的  一边吃饭一边玩友人帐了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.79,0:07:05.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.74,0:07:12.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…别硬拉开  皮肤像针刺一样痛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.49,0:07:15.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我告诉过你吧  夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.50,0:07:17.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字被破坏身体就会裂开
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.96,0:07:19.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烧掉的话身体也会变成灰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.83,0:07:22.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对哦  抱歉了  露神
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.33,0:07:25.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吓死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.28,0:07:30.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这种情况  请你放弃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.23,0:07:31.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.56,0:07:35.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贵志  可以来洗澡了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.53,0:07:36.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.11,0:07:39.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎能如此无情…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.62,0:07:43.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为揭不下来啊  我想还也还不了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.79,0:07:45.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想想办法吧  夏目大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.73,0:07:48.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把名字还给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.04,0:07:50.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法就是没办法嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.00,0:07:53.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目大人！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.49,0:08:05.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露神就住在前面的七森
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.65,0:08:09.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我拿来我就带了  但这东西用来干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.48,0:08:12.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以防万一  反正先收起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.26,0:08:22.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  谢谢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.54,0:08:25.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么  给
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.54,0:08:30.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你的好心  没摔坏的话就拿去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.54,0:08:33.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一个人也吃不了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.43,0:08:36.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢  那我收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.70,0:08:42.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天气真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.90,0:08:46.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.92,0:08:47.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.57,0:08:58.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种时候如果能作出更好的回应
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.33,0:09:00.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真讨厌自己的不善言辞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.58,0:09:03.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个老太太活不长了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.86,0:09:07.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,气息不太美味
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.19,0:09:10.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说失礼的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.39,0:09:17.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是露神的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.73,0:09:19.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  露出这种表情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.54,0:09:22.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露神不只是名字  而是真正的神明啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.82,0:09:27.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你来了啊  夏目大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.67,0:09:32.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了  昨天做了那么多失礼的事  会遭报应的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.59,0:09:34.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲子啊  你怎么做这种遭天谴的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.33,0:09:36.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.76,0:09:40.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙知道你是真正的神明惊慌失措了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.70,0:09:42.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  露神…大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.81,0:09:45.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.43,0:09:51.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然被称为神明  其实以前我是住在这祠堂的无家可归的妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.82,0:09:56.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前这里遭过严重的干旱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.88,0:10:01.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村里的年轻人担忧惨状  向这个祠堂祈愿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.50,0:10:04.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碰巧第二天下雨了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.48,0:10:08.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后村人就把这个祠堂拜为露神
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.54,0:10:11.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还放上很多供品
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.29,0:10:18.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我察觉到时已经充满了力量  身体也变得像样了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.87,0:10:19.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像样了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.35,0:10:22.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前看到他时身体还跟人类一样大
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.21,0:10:25.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在人迹罕至了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.62,0:10:31.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以凭借信仰成长的身体也缩小成这般模样了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.03,0:10:32.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.77,0:10:36.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你桃子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.88,0:10:40.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桃子我也有哦  你看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.90,0:10:42.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那个人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.23,0:10:46.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你见到小花了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.86,0:10:49.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  她叫小花啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.90,0:10:53.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是现在唯一会来这里叩拜的人类
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.79,0:10:58.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此  一起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.61,0:11:04.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  只要把粘在一起的名字也归还掉就不用强行揭开了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.39,0:11:08.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但有一个大问题
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.39,0:11:11.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不认识另一个妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.80,0:11:14.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认识他
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.36,0:11:16.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.91,0:11:19.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,败给玲子后我很不甘心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.15,0:11:27.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说下一个被夺走名字的妖怪后我为了痛快去看过他的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.05,0:11:29.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  画完了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.84,0:11:31.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字虽然不记得了  他是长这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.85,0:11:35.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是他吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.52,0:11:37.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我画得真不错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.18,0:11:40.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有…毛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.17,0:11:43.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有毛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.36,0:11:43.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一根也没有？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.58,0:11:45.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一根也没有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.57,0:11:50.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时他住在参之塚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.70,0:11:53.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是阴影之主  利用阴影移动
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.40,0:11:55.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.77,0:12:05.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑什么  嘲笑我的画吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.29,0:12:12.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们会遭报应的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.70,0:12:23.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们开始在参之塚寻找这只妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.79,0:12:31.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但花了好几天也没能找到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.97,0:12:37.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  好像很困
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.66,0:12:38.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搜索太累了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.23,0:12:40.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.81,0:12:49.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊  小花她看不见
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.30,0:12:52.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明就在能感觉到呼吸的咫尺
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.44,0:12:57.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.02,0:13:00.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也来参拜吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.24,0:13:01.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.58,0:13:07.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  最近好像只有我来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.90,0:13:11.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还怕露神大人寂寞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.96,0:13:14.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您从什么时候开始来参拜的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.71,0:13:15.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从小时候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.22,0:13:21.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请别见笑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.46,0:13:27.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我感觉自己见过一次露神大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.65,0:13:33.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女子学校放学回家路上  也是像今天一样的好天气
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.06,0:13:38.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像平时一样参拜完抬起头时
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.24,0:13:41.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到祠堂后面有一只脚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.98,0:13:44.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然吓了一跳  但我装作没看见
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.12,0:13:51.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后看到戴着老翁面具的人很舒服的坐着
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.18,0:13:55.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说了句今天真是好天气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.39,0:14:00.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我差点就要回答说是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.27,0:14:06.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但感觉到被人类看见露神大人就会消失
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.25,0:14:12.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可现在还在想  如果当时大胆地回答了他就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.63,0:14:16.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为露神大人总是一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.28,0:14:19.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我一定会寂寞难耐了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.59,0:14:22.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以至少应该用声音回应
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.77,0:14:30.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.23,0:14:33.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.39,0:14:35.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个人很寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.58,0:14:37.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个人很痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.33,0:14:42.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个人…很痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.68,0:14:49.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛苦…好重
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.30,0:14:56.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别睡傻了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.56,0:15:04.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚做恶梦了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.84,0:15:06.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是老师太重了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.40,0:15:09.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你的内心有破绽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.40,0:15:11.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,软弱的心会呼唤魔物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.61,0:15:16.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想丢掉性命就时刻不能放松
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.12,0:15:24.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过对我来说还是你早点丢掉性命  让我早点拿到友人帐比较开心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.97,0:15:28.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次再睡傻就拔掉你尾巴上的毛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.16,0:15:29.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这恶魔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.75,0:15:32.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想被妖怪说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.26,0:15:36.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了  夏目大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.07,0:15:39.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.86,0:15:42.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  那家伙果然在这山里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.72,0:15:46.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出声叫他就跑了  但应该还没走远
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.98,0:15:48.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师  兵分两路吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.30,0:15:49.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.37,0:15:50.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.28,0:15:52.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么麻烦的东西来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.14,0:15:53.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.91,0:15:58.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,参上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.24,0:16:14.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,参上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.07,0:16:17.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这家伙  他主动出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.49,0:16:18.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟画完全不一样嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.38,0:16:21.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么蠢话  分明一模一样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.59,0:16:23.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有那个字是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.82,0:16:24.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目  用镜子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.42,0:16:27.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用阳光反射  弄晕他
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.03,0:16:28.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.28,0:16:29.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.58,0:16:32.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,参上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.41,0:16:39.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.50,0:16:43.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,参上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.45,0:16:46.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,参上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.24,0:16:53.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,参上前来取食物
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.24,0:16:55.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,参上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.20,0:16:58.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,参上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.20,0:17:02.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我决胜负吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.59,0:17:07.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赢过我就给你食物
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.81,0:17:10.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者把我吃掉也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.74,0:17:15.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是玲子  你的名字呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.45,0:17:20.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了  他的名字是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.53,0:17:22.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,参上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.58,0:17:24.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.14,0:17:38.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,濯  露神  把名字还给你们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.06,0:17:55.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听见了吗  露神
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.76,0:17:58.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听见了  玲子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.81,0:18:01.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,供品不会一直持续的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.73,0:18:04.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实际上今天就连一个桃子都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.07,0:18:06.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.29,0:18:09.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类就是严厉和无情的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.59,0:18:13.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁着力量还在找个更好的住处比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.63,0:18:16.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你  玲子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.52,0:18:22.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但一旦被爱过  去爱过
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.38,0:18:26.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就无法忘记了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.52,0:18:33.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.24,0:18:40.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经能走路了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.91,0:18:45.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个叫濯的妖怪  利用阴影来到村里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.12,0:18:50.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为拿走剩饭的回报会帮那家人洗完盘子才离开
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.54,0:18:52.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？你调查过了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.09,0:18:55.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在街上连晚上也很明亮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.83,0:18:57.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会再见到他了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.55,0:19:02.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山里也有同伴  跟人类断绝来往  那家伙也轻松了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.18,0:19:05.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  真是那样就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.83,0:19:12.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露神  我带桃子来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.88,0:19:15.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露神？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.12,0:19:17.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里  夏目大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.07,0:19:22.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又变小了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.03,0:19:23.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.42,0:19:30.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你发光了  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.27,0:19:34.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小花走了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.94,0:19:38.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小花长年患病
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.82,0:19:41.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近来一次也不容易了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.53,0:19:49.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小花是最后一个信奉我的人类  她走了的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.46,0:19:50.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.04,0:19:53.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来信奉你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.78,0:19:55.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天来虽然很难  但我也会来叩拜的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.34,0:20:01.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  夏目大人  你是我的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.26,0:20:03.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.03,0:20:06.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能跟小花一起走
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.30,0:20:18.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直  一直仅仅是看着她
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.22,0:20:26.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样终于…终于感觉能够触及她了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.36,0:20:34.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小花她听见了…你的声音  露神
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.11,0:20:38.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你  夏目大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.54,0:20:46.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论以前还是现在  都觉得人类真可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.92,0:21:01.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天天气真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.72,0:21:02.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.44,0:21:07.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.57,0:21:20.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.38,0:21:23.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你干什么啊  好浪费
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.79,0:21:26.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说这种会遭天谴的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.36,0:21:29.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里什么都没有！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.83,0:21:32.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算今天没有  也许明天就有了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.16,0:21:34.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,思念的心最重要
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.34,0:21:43.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么  这只蠢猫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.78,0:21:45.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是招财猫啊  笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.48,0:21:49.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.99,0:21:52.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喵什么喵  把包子还我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.12,0:21:56.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  慢着  包子小偷
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.38,0:21:57.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我的包子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.76,0:22:00.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我买的吧  等等  喂
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.91,0:22:02.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.39,0:22:04.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喵～喵～
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.99,0:23:41.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  夏目  八原的妖怪们哭着说被人类欺负了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.00,0:23:44.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是能看见妖怪的人干的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.47,0:23:46.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙很可疑
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.00,0:23:47.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.30,0:23:50.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是田沼要
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.18,0:23:51.19,biaoti1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(140,550)}八原的怪人
